   E-invoices will be automatically stored in your member carrier by =
default. If you prefer to store invoices in a mobile barcode or Citizen =
Digital Certificate barcode, please update your settings in the Uber App. =
(Note: Once submitted, the updated settings will apply to future =
transactions only and cannot be applied retroactively to past purchases.=
)<br> You may also use the official e-invoice inquiry website to view =
invoice details or to add/update Business ID number, mobile barcode, or =
donation code. Any addition or update must be completed within 7 days from =
the invoice issuance date and can only be done once.<br> Please note: Uber =
users whose app registration is outside Taiwan cannot store e-invoices =
using a mobile barcode or Citizen Digital Certificate barcode. In such =
cases, the invoice can only be stored in the member carrier. Please ensure =
your account email address is up to date.
                            </li>
                            <li style=3D"padding: 0 0 5px 0;">
                                The Ibon printing function (for non-winning=
 invoices) will be available starting on the 8th day after the invoice =
issue date and will close on the 6th of every odd-numbered month (e.g., =
January, March, May, etc.). If your transaction was with RT-Mart, Pizza Hut=
, KFC, Watsons, or PX Mart, please refer to the remarks below for specific =
instructions.<br> Once your print request is successfully submitted, you =
will receive an email. Please follow the instructions in the email to print=
 your e-invoice copy at an 7-Eleven ibon kiosk.<br> Reminder : After =
receiving the confirmation email, please proceed to print your invoice as =
soon as possible. Consumers are responsible for the safekeeping of their =
printed e-invoice copies and for redeeming any prizes.
